Maintenance Software is an Australian made CMMS that is based in Brisbane. Our
software solution has helped asset-intensive businesses track maintenance for
over 30 years and continues to be at the forefront of the Maintenance Software
industry.

The MEX Support Department are responsible for providing front line customer
service for operational and technical issues relating to the MEX software.
Working with a large customer base across a number of industries and
countries.

We are currently in the market for an enthusiastic Support Person to join our
team.

